.Sh NAME
.Nm dehtml
.Nd extract text from HTML
.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl s
.Op Ar
.
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility extracts text
from HTML documents.
Text inside
.Sy <title> ,
.Sy <style>
and
.Sy <script>
tags is discarded.
Numeric and common named HTML entities
are converted.
.
.Pp
The arguments are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl s
Collapse whitespace outside of
.Sy <pre>
tags.
.El
.
.Sh BUGS
There is no way to extract image alt text.
